//XA
GRAB 301
LINK 800

MARK READ
TEST EOF
TJMP TERMINATE
COPY F #DIAL
ADDI X 1 X
TEST X > 10
FJMP READ

REPL GO
MODE
MARK WAIT
TEST MRD
FJMP WAIT

COPY M X 
COPY -1 #DIAL
MODE
JUMP READ

MARK GO
LINK 800
GRAB 200

MARK WRITE
COPY M F
COPY M F
TEST EOF
FJMP WRITE
DROP 
LINK -1
MODE
COPY 0 M
HALT

MARK TERMINATE
LINK -1
KILL
HALT

//XB
GRAB 300

MARK WRITESONG
COPY F M
COPY F M
SEEK -9999
JUMP WRITESONG
